section.para:
The View menu allows

             to zoom (zoom In or Out);
            to divide the window and get two independant windows (one with the graph, the other with the complementary information);
            to display the edge names (pairs formed by the source and the target names);
            to display/hide the grid and the mini-map.


                View menu

The current functionalities are:

            animate the associate regulatory graph by selecting a path;
            search a path between two given states (intermediary can also be specified).
